"Guide Quick Start Text" = "1. Open Sources. 2. Import an existing repository folder such as /var/mobile/Documents/my-repo, or create a new source. 3. Switch the active source from the source list.";
"Guide Source Text" = "Edit source name, description, author, Base URL, scheme and architecture from Sources > Edit Source. Author defaults to DaFei. App targets stay arm64.";
"Guide Package Text" = "Use Packages > Import Deb to copy one deb into public/debs and rebuild the index with dpkg-scanpackages. Edit Control and Icon repacks the deb, then rebuilds Packages.";
"Guide Publish Text" = "Configure an SSH remote, branch, username and email, then Push GitHub. RepoKit uses /var/mobile/.ssh/id_ed25519 and auto-builds the index before committing.";
"Guide Troubleshooting Text" = "If deb import fails, verify the file exists under /var/mobile or /var/jb/var/mobile. If counts look wrong, rebuild the index and read the dpkg-scanpackages output. Run Check Source before publishing.";
